Scored byTestilo, procedure tsp24
Digested byTestilo, procedure tdp24

Introduction

This is a digest of results from a battery of accessibility Tests.

The battery includes 1353 automated accessibility tests drawn from ten different packages: Alfa, Axe, Continuum, Equal Access, HTML CodeSniffer, Nu Html Checker, QualWeb, Tenon, Testaro, and WAVE.

These tests were run on the web page named above and gave the page a score of 1866, where 0 would be perfect.

Issue summary

Special issues

log: Score 600. This is based on the amount of browser error logging and miscellaneous logging during the tests.

solos: Score 10. This is based on issues reported by unclassified tests. Details are in the report.

Classified issues

Issue contentBeyondLandmarks

WCAG: 1.3.6

Score: 251

Issue reports in this category:

  • Package alfa, test r57, score 198 (Perceivable text content is not included in any landmark)
  • Package axe, test region, score 12 (Some page content is not contained by landmarks)
  • Package ibm, test Rpt_Aria_OrphanedContent_Native_Host_Sematics, score 116 (Content does not reside within an element with a landmark role)

Issue overflowHidden

WCAG: 1.4.4

Score: 99

Issue reports in this category:

  • Package qualWeb, test QW-ACT-R40, score 97 (Zoomed text node is clipped by a CSS overflow declaration)

Issue menuNavigation

WCAG: 2.1.1

Score: 92

Issue reports in this category:

  • Package testaro, test menuNav, score 90 (Nonstandard keyboard navigation among focusable menu items)

Issue leadingInsufficient

WCAG: 1.4.8

Score: 84

Issue reports in this category:

  • Package alfa, test r73, score 82 (Paragraph of text has insufficient line height)

Issue leadingClipsText

WCAG: 1.4.8

Score: 78

Issue reports in this category:

  • Package tenon, test 144, score 76 (Line height is insufficent to properly display the computed font size)

Issue hoverSurprise

WCAG: 1.4.13

Score: 72

Issue reports in this category:

  • Package testaro, test hover, score 70 (Hovering is mis-indicated or changes content)

Issue focusIndication

WCAG: 2.4.7

Score: 71

Issue reports in this category:

  • Package testaro, test focInd, score 6 (Focused element displays no or a nostandard focus indicator)
  • Package alfa, test r65, score 2 (Element in the sequential focus order has no visible focus)
  • Package qualWeb, test QW-ACT-R62, score 66 (Element in the sequential focus order has no visible focus)

Issue linkIndication

WCAG: 1.3.3

Score: 71

Issue reports in this category:

  • Package testaro, test linkUl, score 67 (Non-underlined adjacent links)
  • Package alfa, test r62, score 2 (Inline link is not distinct from the surrounding text except by color)
  • Package axe, test link-in-text-block, score 3 (Link is not distinct from surrounding text without reliance on color)

WCAG: 1.4.3

Score: 57

  • Package htmlcs, test e:AAA.1_4_6.G18.Fail, score 12 (Contrast between the text and its background is less than 4.5:1)
